<plot>Brian, a young boy growing up in a disfunctional home journeys outside one day to a world full of new and exciting adventures. After finding an old baseball and glove he realizes what his direction in life will be. With the help of an old stray dog, Brian soon learns that the most important thing about the Dog Days of summer, is having a best friend to share it with.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?153925</url></doc>
